HEADWORD: Repealer
<hw>Re*peal"er</hw> <pr>(-?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who repeals;
one who seeks a repeal; specifically, an advocate for the repeal of the
Articles of Union between Great Britain and Ireland.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

